      "about": "These two tracks mark another turning point for me, not in the sense of perfection achieved, but in the sense of clarity found. They brought me closer to the sound I've been reaching for: a vision of what my music should feel like, not just only what it should sound like.\n\nTo the casual listener, this may be two ambient pieces. To me, it's another step along a path I've been walking for years, toward something harder to name but easier to feel. I'm coming closer!\n\nListen closely. The details are there for those who seek them.",
