      "year": "2024",
      "genre": "Ambient / Dark Ambient / Soundscape",
      "about": "It is finally done.\n\nMy first album, with many tracks that I have exclusively created for my YouTube project over the last few months, is finally ready to see the world.\n\nI'm feeling a bit of a \"Back to The Roots\" vibe because some of the tracks sound like me in 2019, only in a better version.\n\nOverall, I am very satisfied and hope you share the album enthusiastically. It was a long journey to get here, and I feel like it's just beginning to really take off.\n\nAnd most importantly: Without YOU, none of this would have been possible. Everything I wanted to achieve was to bring something into this world that offers each of you a moment of personal peace, in a world that seems to almost spin out of control.",
